# Public Tenant Site

## Tenant Resolution

Layout reads `x-tenant-slug` / `x-tenant-host` headers (set by middleware).
Always check `verified: true` for custom domain lookups.

## Blocks

Pages are arrays of blocks stored as JSON. Block types: hero, text, image, gallery, cta, contactForm, spacer, html, postsGrid.

`BlockRenderer` parses JSON and maps to components in `components/tenant/blocks/`.

## Styling

- Use CSS variable `var(--tenant-primary)` for tenant brand color
- Set in layout via `style={{ '--tenant-primary': primaryColor }}`
- Responsive: mobile-first with Tailwind breakpoints
